{"tid":800532,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人做ERP consultant","createTime":"2018-08-31T03:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T18:44:51.000Z","uid":68080,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"977383ff3f8ff8f8f844e1737a55132f2251266f","tid":800532,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"我大學就有個operations management major<br />\n雖然都叫讀過一兩個關於erp crm既course 但係對係香港既職業前景都唔係太清楚<br />\n而且除左好basic 既excel vba之外 咩programming language都唔識<br />\n<br />\n前排見有間公司請erp consultant 咁就上去interview試下<br />\n都講清楚我既情況 但係間公司又俾個offer我<br />\n<br />\n而家想請問下做唔同erp 既前景，人工，進修<br />\n1, 做唔同erp 或者 crm software既前景係咪好大差別，salesforce，SAP，oracle，netsuite<br />\n2, 行頭又點<br />\n3, 又有咩可以進修"},{"pid":"869dd9818a00887157868d0265fdb16c8859765e","tid":800532,"uid":155254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"ERP前景一片光明<br />\n要睇兩方面<br />\n<br />\n選對功能組別  - 例如CRM, Finance, Procurement, Human Resource, Supply Chain, and Accounting. 點揀就要睇需求, 自己能力同興趣<br />\n<br />\n軟件平台 - Oracle (PeopleSoft, E-Business Suite, JD Edwards), SAP, Salesforce, ServiceNow, Microsoft (Dynamics 365). 點揀都係要睇需求, 自己能力同興趣. 大路就 Oracle and SAP. ServiceNow响外國都好hit"},{"pid":"dc6c95dae05fe0e0b65726f04ebad4fa9c93e185","tid":800532,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"869dd9818a00887157868d0265fdb16c8859765e","tid":800532,"uid":155254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"ERP前景一片光明<br />\n要睇兩方面<br />\n<br />\n選對功能組別  - 例如CRM, Finance, Procurement, Human Resource, Supply Chain, and Accounting. 點揀就要睇需求, 自己能力同興趣<br />\n<br />\n軟件平台 - Oracle (PeopleSoft, E-Business Suite, JD Edwards), SAP, Salesforce, ServiceNow, Microsoft (Dynamics 365). 點揀都係要睇需求, 自己能力同興趣. 大路就 Oracle and SAP. ServiceNow响外國都好hit"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"多謝ching先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人比較有興趣做crm 類似salesforce<br />\n平時需要做咩<br />\n咁對一個新人 你有咪建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a25a04d8cf5fd55ba5bb7f980ea7fc0ca7c6da","tid":800532,"uid":155254,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"Gartner CRM Magic Quadrant 2018<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/131647_e9dfe7db3eee9fc6251c69af2ae27108.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F131647_e9dfe7db3eee9fc6251c69af2ae27108.png&h=e6e3426f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家好多CRM都係Software As a Service<br />\n平時會做 requirement analysis, CRM tool configuration, 同 testing 多<br />\n一個新人好好學習就得啦, 多做多學, Be an expert on something<br />\n<br />\n酒呢?"},{"pid":"b17466b963c4214a0e643013e76e9a4af289c90b","tid":800532,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3a25a04d8cf5fd55ba5bb7f980ea7fc0ca7c6da","tid":800532,"uid":155254,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"Gartner CRM Magic Quadrant 2018<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/131647_e9dfe7db3eee9fc6251c69af2ae27108.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F131647_e9dfe7db3eee9fc6251c69af2ae27108.png&h=e6e3426f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家好多CRM都係Software As a Service<br />\n平時會做 requirement analysis, CRM tool configuration, 同 testing 多<br />\n一個新人好好學習就得啦, 多做多學, Be an expert on something<br />\n<br />\n酒呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d757df0462e97dd7cab7ae531411b2c350bc4b","tid":800532,"uid":192623,"like":0,